Package: libfuse2
Section: libs
Priority: optional
Architecture: ARCH
Depends: libc (>= 1.1.8), ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: provides FUSE API functions.
 FUSE (Filesystem in Userspace) is an interface for userspace programs 
 to export a filesystem to the Linux kernel.
 .
 This package provides libfuse, a shared library which contains FUSE 
 API functions.

